snippet.title: ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER | Match Three Pirates II | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Enjoy the great Match 3 Pirate Adventure. Build your own Pirate Theme park on your own island, form groups of three or more crabs, canons, steering wheels, explosives and other pirate items to unlock powerful boosters and complete all level goals. 

Available on Nintendo Switch and Steam on 20 December 2021
